SIMPLE: thereafter
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thereafter
<hw>There*af"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>⟦edh⟧⟦aemac⟧r⟦ae⟧fter</ets> after that. See <er>There</er>, and
<er>After</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>After that; afterward.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>According to that; accordingly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I deny not but that it is of greatest concernment in the church
and commonwealth to have a vigilant eye how books demean themselves as
well as men; and <qex>thereafter</qex> to confine, imprison, and do
sharpest justice on them as malefactors.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Of that sort.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧My
audience is not <xex>thereafter</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thereagain</ent>⟦br⟧
